<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪在走廊里看到伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她觉得伊坦比其他男生友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她希望有一天可以和他做搭档。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>体育馆里，邓恩老师坐在桌边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些细绳是用来做什么的？” 伊坦问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要做友情手链。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“友情手链。” 莉琪想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以做一个给——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“手链是女孩子戴的！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是的。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在我加利福尼亚的那个学校，每个人都戴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我姐姐和她的朋友们戴友情手链。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得很可笑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一点儿都不可笑。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一种表达友情的方式。” 他看着波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果有朋友送你一条手链，你不能剪断它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要你们还是朋友，就要一直戴着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经等不及了！” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先选三种颜色。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真好看。” 莉琪想拿蓝色的细绳，伊坦也想拿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两只手碰到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。” 伊坦小声说，“我选另一个吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以选同一种颜色。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，剪六十厘米下来，然后把剩下的给伊坦吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家量好并剪下六条细绳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，邓恩老师告诉他们怎么做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在一端的十厘米处打个结。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，把这一端贴在桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，按颜色分好细绳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每种颜色要有两条细绳。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好了！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从最左边的细绳开始编。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用它在每一条细绳上都打结后，再从左边开始。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明白了吗？” 邓恩老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明白了！” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她觉得需要编很长时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她想今天就编完。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开始编吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果需要帮忙，可以叫我。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的是做给你的。” 尼娜小声对莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪看着她，咽了一口口水。“谢谢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她接着编。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>编呀、编呀、编呀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她终于编好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她感觉手很酸，脖子也很疼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是手链看上去很不错。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了。该出去踢足垒球了。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你的手链还没做好，可以带回家做。” 邓恩老师补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，他看到莉琪的手链。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做得好，莉琪。” 他说，“你今天非常努力。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她做好了手链，很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>东西都整理好以后，孩子们排队准备出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪站在伊坦的后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到伊坦把还没编好的手链放进口袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伊坦。” 莉琪叫他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的手链是做给你的。你会戴吗？” 她小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。谢谢你，真的很好看。” 他告诉莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪笑着把手链戴在他的手腕上，然后跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>